    <h1>Neuromarketing</h1>
    <p class="description">The application of neuroscience principles to understand how consumers make buying decisions at the subconscious level. It explains why people buy what they buy — and how to design marketing that works with the brain rather than against it.</p>
    <div class="post-meta">
      <div class="meta-author">
        <div class="meta-avatar">AVR</div>
        <div class="meta-author-info">
